# DocScope Frontend - Development Context

## Project Summary
Modern, dark-themed document security scanner UI. Single page application feel with multiple HTML pages. Heavy emphasis on visual polish, animations, and attention to detail.

## Design Philosophy
- Dark glassmorphism aesthetic
- Neon accent colors
- Custom cursor
- Smooth micro-interactions
- Professional but futuristic

